---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import hero from '../assets/voices-hero.webp';
---

<Base
  title="Voices of Resilience"
  description="In-depth conversations with returning citizens who have navigated reentry successfully — stories of triumph, practical wisdom, and life after incarceration."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pt-20 md:px-8">
    <p class="eyebrow">Community · Voices of Resilience</p>
    <h1 class="mt-4 text-5xl md:text-6xl" style='font-variation-settings: "opsz" 144, "SOFT" 50, "WONK" 1;'>
      Returning citizen stories.
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg text-muted">
      In this section, I amplify the powerful voices of other returning citizens who have not only
      navigated reentry successfully but are truly thriving — raw honesty, hard-won wisdom, and
      lives transformed against formidable odds.
    </p>
    <hr class="horizon mt-10" />
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 py-12 md:px-8">
    <div class="prose-rcj">
      <Image
        src={hero}
        alt="Mountain sunset"
        widths={[768, 1280]}
        sizes="(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 768px"
        class="rounded-md"
      />

      <h2>Beyond the Stereotypes</h2>
      <p>
        Too often, the narrative surrounding incarceration and reentry focuses solely on challenges
        or deficits. But the reality is far richer and more inspiring. These stories challenge those
        stereotypes, showcasing the immense capacity for growth, resilience, and positive
        contribution. Each voice here offers a unique perspective on overcoming systemic barriers,
        personal struggles, and societal stigmas — proving that a meaningful, fulfilling life after
        prison is not just possible, but being lived every day.
      </p>

      <h2>Lessons from the Journey Back</h2>
      <p>
        Through in-depth conversations, I delve beyond the headlines to explore the practicalities
        and personal fortitude that define successful reintegration. These stories are rich with
        invaluable lessons: specific strategies for securing housing and employment, insights into
        rebuilding family relationships, and advice on navigating mental health and community
        engagement. Their collective wisdom shines a light on what truly helps — and sometimes
        hinders — the journey back.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pb-4 md:px-8">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-6">Episodes</p>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <iframe
        style="border-radius:12px"
        src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/2pq6Pc2FMzg2exuxwyPWp1?utm_source=generator"
        width="100%"
        height="232"
        frameborder="0"
        allowfullscreen
        allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture"
        loading="lazy"
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-5 pb-20 pt-12 md:px-8">
    <hr class="horizon" />
    <p class="mt-8 text-muted">
      More conversations are on the way. If you're a returning citizen with a story to share,
      <a href="mailto:brett@rcjourney.cloud">reach out</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>
